{"tid":1683750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記協邀謝振中出席交流會　謝稱忙於處理示威未能出席","createTime":"2019-10-30T18:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T18:47:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8828037646cbaeb4d910ff15e62a06fdc29275d4","tid":1683750,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"近月示威和警民衝突中，警方處理前線記者的手法多次引發爭議，香港記者協會星期六（11 月 2 日）舉行「槍林彈雨下的香港」交流會，邀請警察公共關係科總警司謝振中出席，和前線記者交流，但謝振中指由於當日忙於應付遊行集會未能出席，記協表示失望，「將於會場敬備空櫈一張，虛位以待以示尊重」。<br />\n<br />\n記協指，謝振中回覆時稱 6 月至今多次與不同傳媒組織會面，但記協自 6 月 11 日和謝振中面會後，一直未有和他見面商討，今次邀請他和前線記協交流，他亦未能出席，令前線記者失去機會向他反映採訪難處，非常可惜。<br />\n<br />\n記者又指，謝振中稱要待反修例示威完結後才能安排警員和傳媒組織交流，「此舉無異賊過興兵」，認為在衝突期間警方與傳媒交流方能減少誤會衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/74306040_10157458778215309_2920026463572852736_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQkqeaaQSSvGFZDOxGh-h59wy7GnU-2i0dnFWCVKTDsyn8FMKA5zUNRVn1BmJwr8dfg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=fb2f5a23c240b4f6271ac9d394b969c1&amp;oe=5E5D3CDD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F74306040_10157458778215309_2920026463572852736_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQkqeaaQSSvGFZDOxGh-h59wy7GnU-2i0dnFWCVKTDsyn8FMKA5zUNRVn1BmJwr8dfg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dfb2f5a23c240b4f6271ac9d394b969c1%26oe%3D5E5D3CDD&h=a2e4de06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d09f9fb90cc0c8ad505f132a8ae5f48f1a75796","tid":1683750,"uid":41545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:40:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾都無咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba76463302fc58b1602c491e9d503b3bd7d85da","tid":1683750,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:42:37.000Z","msg":